<br>
But, the gist of that was that grps don't want wizards in general. (And if it was just me making that claim, you'd be right to dismiss me as a nut case, but MANY, MANY wizards have had this problem, and posted about it here, so it clearly can't be just me, so don't even go down that road)<br>
<br>
Many people suggested that I solo.. And while I can't quite solo in High XP zones, I did find a zone where a Druid friend and I could pair and kite mobs for good XP,  HoH. And what does SOE do? They change the zone so that random mobs summon, effectively making caster fighting ( kiting ) impractical here.<br>
<br>
Isn't it about time that the over-optimists here realize that SOE is deliberatly nerfing soloing? They want and expect people to grp to hunt. That's the core design of the game!! <br>
<br>
But, since they won't give wizards anything that makes grps want us, by doing that, they are nerfing us, in comparison to other classes<br>
<br>
Actually, they are not only nerfiing us.. they are nerfing any class that isn't among the holy trinity of Tank/Healer/Slower.<br>
 <br>
I'm probably not gonna reply to this thread, as I've said, I'm sick to death arguing about it, but I just felt I had to vent after the nerfing of HoH,and who knows where else. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=annoid>Annoid</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0> at: 4/25/03 6:10:49 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=azzitay>Azzitay</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br>  Posts: 213<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/25/03 7:27 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: You still say Wizards aren't broken? They are nerfing us</span><hr size=1> Correct.<br>
