<br>
But the problem is more for the average wizard, they lack the power to do well in a group. Most of them lack ft items, lack spells, don't have pp for a horsie. (pls don't respond it's easy to farm stuff. Farming is only easy, if you waste a lot of time on this game and the average wizards are mostly not the hardcore players. so farming takes an awfull lot of their playing time)<br>
<br>
First: i would like to see, that soe, made wizards do critical 2x dam from the start and that the aa only increases the chances then. In this way lower lvl wizzies are upgraded a bit, while it doesn't make wizzies unbalanced(wizzies with loads of aa in crit aaskills, just stay the same)<br>
<br>
Second, give wizzies from low lvl on, some focus buffs, self only or group, like eci-flame. So for the wizards lacking the good lvl 60 spells, can improve their lower lvl nukes.<br>
<br>
Third, make those research runes drop more? They are really rare i think.<br>
<br>
Fourth, group version spells of yonder, mass invis, mass levitation.<br>
<br>
Five: put more CASTER mobs into the different xp zones. Random spawning caster mobs, make a wizard more usefull in groups. As long as groups can xp in zones without ANY caster mob spawning randomly, our burst damage is not really wanted.<br>
