Cristoban, please leave the snotty comments to the other wizards.  I am happy you are not having troubles finding groups, but even in BoT groups are leaning toward back up healing, slowing, charm &amp; pet damage, and crowd control over nuking damage.  Until nuke damage is just as attractive as these factors, wizards are going to have a more difficult time finding a group.<br>
